    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Plans that outline the significance of a heritage asset, such as a church or other built work, and that outline the course of its conservation and management. Plans set out in the CMP include its significance for future use, along with a description of repairs or alterations. The compilation of a CMP involves the collaboration of various professions and stakeholders.</Note_Text>
